nre, using it as a vehicle for political protest and social commentary."], "scores": [0.804115038530926, 0.614182175759844, 0.6114902531110749, 0.5921626132923289, 0.5872331524291479], "model_name": "bge-large", "document_ids": ["Jazz", "Blues", "Funk", "House", "Afrobeat"]}}